agg.attribute
Interface AttrEvent

All Known Subinterfaces:
AttrViewEvent
All Known Implementing Classes:
TupleEvent, TupleViewEvent
public interface AttrEvent

Attribute event interface for delivering information about attribute changes to clients.

See Also:
AttrTuple
